data.name: label6.Text
data.value: Use "-" to indicate the starting and ending page numbers. Multiple page numbers can be separated by ";", "," or " " (space), such as "1;4-15;2 56", which means to extract sequentially Contents on pages 1, 4 to 15, 2 and 56. Do not refer to Extract the content of all pages of the source file when setting page numbers.
